# Data

## Benchmark: `legalrag_qa_benchmark.csv`
242 complexity-annotated Kazakh legal QA questions
(182 answerable + 60 unanswerable). Columns: question, gold_answer,
gold_chunk_id, complexity, answerability, question_type, domain.

## Corpus: LegalRAG (Hugging Face)
56,916 structure-aware chunks from 5,603 legal documents.
https://huggingface.co/datasets/Arailym-tleubayeva/LegalRAG

Columns: doc_id, date, section_title, source, chunk_id, text,
words, char_len, word_len, normalized_text.

**Note:** BM25 retrieval uses the `text` column. License: CC BY 4.0.
